  "format": "Sean, Amanda, and Chris Ryan review 'The Bone Temple,' Nia DaCosta's follow-up to '28 Years Later,' then build an ad-hoc Ralph Fiennes hall of fame. Plus: Mona Fastvold on 'The Testament of Ann Lee.'",
  "segments": [
